		<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#2c3e50] mb-4">Upcoming Events</h2>
		<p class="text-[#34495e] text-base leading-relaxed m-0">
			Join us for our weekly Sunday service at 10:00 AM. All are welcome to experience the love and grace of God in our community.
		</p>
	</div> -->
</div>
